Class ObjectReader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.azrael.ObjectReader<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The format to which the object has been written
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CloneReader, JsonReader, XmlReader

    public abstract class ObjectReader<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Reads the content of an object in a given format, to recreate the corresponding instance.
